\begin{eg}{San Diego to Las Vegas}\label{eg:sdvegas}
\egquestion
 Given the $\Delta x$ and $\Delta y$ values from the previous examples, 
find the $\Delta x$ and $\Delta y$ from San Diego to Las Vegas.

